    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically sound E92 M3 featuring the iconic S65B40 4.0L naturally aspirated V8. This unit exhibits a linear power band and crisp throttle response, peaking at an 8,400 RPM redline. The drivetrain is paired with a 7-speed M-DCT dual-clutch transmission and an M Variable Differential Lock for superior traction out of corners. Significant preventative maintenance has been addressed, including rod bearing replacement with VAC treated shells and upgraded throttle actuators. The suspension retains its Electronic Damper Control (EDC) functionality, providing adjustable damping rates for varied tarmac conditions. This is a well-sorted enthusiast's example with a clean subframe and robust cooling system, ready for spirited driving.",
